{"tid":121214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞裔工人墮地傷重不治","createTime":"2017-02-15T05:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T16:53:23.000Z","uid":3716,"like":71,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"173dc95f4f987d71573f64e95dbee2c304a2b862","tid":121214,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170215/s00001/1487133020219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170215%2Fs00001%2F1487133020219&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=634cc0dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170215%2Fs00001%2F1487133020219&h=87fa5079\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170215/s00001/1487133020219</a><br />\n<br />\n【奪命意外】AIA嘉年華塌工作台　拆場南亞裔工人墮地傷重不治<br />\n<br />\n在中環龍和道舉行的「AIA歐陸嘉年華2016」，於剛過去的周日結束，今早發生奪命工業意外，一名男工友清拆時從工作台墮下身亡。<br />\n<br />\n事發早上10時許，一班工人在清拆場內的機動遊戲，其中一名南亞裔工人，在工作台上拆卸過山車支架時，工作台突然塌下，工人從約6米高墮地，重傷昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n救護員到場將傷者送院搶救，最終證實不治。警方到場封鎖現場調查。"},{"pid":"47ade7337a0c40e787da047821df59c5255444d9","tid":121214,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10720e6bba3953b767eb5bc10df7968e04c881ab","tid":121214,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:13:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a54add12ab74c58f382c831ba71b91feae31cf6","tid":121214,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ae88e6258754c64f09009c5b412268286836c3","tid":121214,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20